**EmotiBot** is an empathetic, conversational AI designed to support users through mental health challenges, casual emotional check-ins, or just a friendly chat. Powered by **LangGraph**, **Gemini 2.0 Flash**, and integrated with **LangChain tools**, EmotiBot delivers human-like, emotionally intelligent conversations tailored to the userâ€™s emotional state.

### Set up your API key

If you don't already have an API key, you can grab one from [AI Studio](https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey). You can find [detailed instructions in the docs](https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/api-key).


